We also encourage our people to achieve a balance between work and caring for relatives. As this topic continues to grow in importance, we will support our people in Germany who provide care for close family members. We offer a variety of support options through the Elder Care program. This pro- gram is based on four pillars: time off work and flexible working, communication, counseling, and training on health matters.

